<br>
------------------ EQ Forums ------------------<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>General Discussion</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- all non-specific EQ chat<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Apprentices' Hall</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- Newbie forum, links to newbie guides, etc.<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Sorcerers' Tower</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- End Game discussion {Nadiar's original name made me think it was a spell/quest discussion forum}<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Spells &amp; AA</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- self explanatory<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>PvP Discussion and Tactics</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- self explanatory<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Class Balancing</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- self explanatory<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Equipment Advice</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- Area to ask about gear questions<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Quester's Assistant</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- For any questions related to a guide, or a quest.<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Tales of Sorcery</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- In character stories {added, cuz some people like these}<br>
------------------ OT Forums ------------------<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Off Topic Forum</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- self explanatory<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Polls Forum</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- self explanatory<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Rant Forum</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> -- self explanatory <br>
